Dark in a furry shoulder Rushes at Flashing.

FlashingConvoy get checked by dark into a mountain side causing a crater as 
Flash tries to stand. "That's it Beast mode" enters His Lion beast mode and 
leaps at Dark with his claws out.
 
Dark in shock that he is still on his feet as the Lion as it hits him clawing 
his breast plate. 

Flashing tries sinks his teeth into darks Shoulder plate trying to tear it 
off.

Dark Rears in pain as he shoulder plate is removed

Flashing Jumps off "Maximize" as in midair he turn back in to Robot mode. 
"Come On."  As he lands A the piece of dark shoulder falls to the ground.

Dark tries to sweep Flashing legs.

Flashing falls on his back. 

As dark jumps up and tries to slam his fist in to flashing chest.

Flashing Rolls back barely as darks punch miss.

Dark fist slams into the earth causing it to crack and rocks fly up. As Dark 
takes to the air. 

Flashing Flips up to his feet.
